Okay.

01:15:29.120 --> 01:15:29.360
‘My’.

01:15:30.080 --> 01:15:33.440
We use ‘my’ to show that something belongs to me.

01:15:34.160 --> 01:15:34.640
Okay.

01:15:35.840 --> 01:15:36.240
