‘you are’ ‘you’re’.

01:17:00.640 --> 01:17:01.360
Okay.

01:17:01.360 --> 01:17:05.520
So make sure you use this one to show possession.

01:17:05.520 --> 01:17:06.240
Okay.

01:17:06.240 --> 01:17:11.280
