01:41:19.120 --> 01:41:23.440
So, I have to say, “The girl is pretty.”

01:41:24.880 --> 01:41:26.320
And the last example.

01:41:27.040 --> 01:41:29.280
“I can see ___ sky.”

01:41:30.560 --> 01:41:32.720
Now, we only have one sky.

01:41:33.280 --> 01:41:33.840
Right…

01:41:33.840 --> 01:41:38.960
So, if there’s only one and only, we have
to put the article ‘the’.

01:41:39.920 --> 01:41:42.400
“I can see the sky.”

01:41:43.840 --> 01:41:44.560
Okay.

01:41:44.560 --> 01:41:50.080
So in this video, we talked about the articles
‘a’, ‘an’ and ‘the’.

01:41:50.080 --> 01:41:53.280
