03:33:43.120 --> 03:33:46.319
‘We has been riding bikes to school recently.’

03:33:47.040 --> 03:33:49.040
What's the mistake in this sentence?

03:33:50.399 --> 03:33:51.920
The subject here is ‘We’.

03:33:52.720 --> 03:33:58.880
For ‘I’, ‘you’, ‘we’ and ‘they’,
we have to say ‘have been’, not ‘has

